accessibility.text: Main Goal: Photograph the most beautiful spots in the city
Christof is a profissional photographer and wants to capture the best sights and spots in the city, and so he decides to visit the Torre dos Clrigos
As he is staying at the Porto Antas Hotel, he needs to catch the metro at the Estdio do Drago station

Its the first day of Christofs staying at Porto, so he needs to purchase a ticket to ride the metro. He knows there is a 3-day pass targeted at people who are staying just a few days in the city, but he isnt able to find information about that in the station

After 30 minutes trying to figure out which ticket corresponds to the said 3-day pass at the ticket vending machine, and knowing there arent any physical barriers, Christof enters the metro without a valid ticket

He decides to ask for help in the Aliados station, as there is nearby a tourism office that can help him. He finally figures out which ticket to buy and, on the way back to the hotel, he buys and validates the correct ticket
